text.div: Repeat Prescription required within 12 hours (Dx86) <br/> <br/> Selected service: Lloyds Pharmacy, Stokewood Close, Fair Oak, Eastle<br/>
Prescription request<br/>Not enough medication until surgery opens<br/>No medication available<br/>Next dose due within next 12 hours<br/>

Reason for call menu - continued to next list.<br/>A prescription request was the main reason for the contact.<br/>The main reason for the contact was not a new or worsening illness.<br/>The individual did not have enough medication to last until the surgery next opened.<br/>The medication was suitable for repeat prescribing without further consultation.<br/>The individual had no medication available.<br/>The next dose was due within 12 hours.<br/>Instructions given were: The individual needs a repeat prescription.<br/>Directory of Services referral: Lloyds Pharmacy, Stokewood Close, Fair Oak, Eastleigh<br/>
IF THE RECOMMENDED TIMEFRAME FALLS OUTSIDE OPENING HOURS: I will arrange for a clinician to speak to the individual.<br/> <br/>
